        "timestamp": "2018-04-12 18:14:44.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified+1\n\nThe latest change to the deployment spec will fix a bug in the livenessProbe configuration that will allow it to dynamically be disbled so the pod does not restart.  This will allow for troubleshooting.\n\nMake use of that feature like this in your own values.yaml (with everything else enabled: false) \n\nportal:\n  enabled: true\n  portal-cassandra:\n    liveness:\n      enabled: false\n\nOr directly on the command line like this:\n\nhelm install local/onap --name dev --namespace onap --set portal.portal-cassandra.liveness.enabled=false -f ~/onap-envs/dev-values.yaml --debug\n\ndev-portal-cassandra-65c975c647-g9w9w   0/1       Running     0          8m",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
